title: Georgi Gurtskaya
text:
Georgi Dzhustanovich Gurtskaya (; born 30 January 1986) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> in 2004 for <a href="FC%20Dynamo%20Moscow">FC Dynamo Moscow</a>.
